g.aria-label: A simple DuckyScript powered USB attack platform.
Power on your USB Nugget via USB Type C. It should pop up as a flash drive on your computer named "Nugget".
Edit and save files over USB. Use the built-in screen & buttons to quickly run attack payloads with our cat-themed interface!
For remote access, connect to the Nugget WiFi AP using password "nugget123". Just open 192.168.4.1 in a web browser!
